        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p class="align-left">
            Send us your requirements and a dedicated personal assistant (PA) will be assigned to you. PA will contact you to understand all your requirements.
            <br></br>
        </p>
        <div class="listmessage">
            <p class="align-left">
                <ol>
                    <li>PA will research on your behalf and will talk to brokers and agents.</li>
                    <li>PA will share research, policy details and options with you. You choose the best option.</li>
                    <li>PA will assist you and your family with the buying process.</li>
                </ol>
            </p>
        </div>
        <p>
            <br>
            You pay a flat fee of $29 for a personal assistance service.
            <br><br>
            We also assist you with claims<br>
            please contact us in advance before availing medical services. You will need to fill a authorization form so we can legally work on your behalf and assist you with the calim process. We only get paid if the claim is approved. Our fee is $29 or 3.5% of the approved claim amount, whichever is higher.
        </p>
    </div>
